                    "text": "In my opinion, Phạm Tiến Dũng Gia Sư will complement rather than replace teachers. While machines are incredibly efficient at data processing and automated grading, they lack the 'human touch' which is essential for fostering a positive learning environment and providing moral guidance to young learners.",
